OL,3,CCalls for tougher regulation after
OL,4,Conline grooming crimes reach record
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FMore than 7,000 sexual communication
OL,8,Fwith a child offences were recorded
OL,9,Flast year, with criminals frequently
OL,10,Fusing Snapchat and Whatsapp to find
OL,11,Fvictims
OL,13,FOnline grooming crimes have reached
OL,14,Frecord levels in the UK, with more
OL,15,Fthan 7,000 offences recorded by police
OL,16,Fover the last year for the first time,
OL,17,Fthe NSPCC has said.
