OL,3,CCalls for tougher regulation after
OL,4,Conline grooming crimes reach record
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FThe charity has asked the government
OL,8,Fto introduce "ambitious regulation"
OL,9,Fand strengthen the Online Safety Act
OL,10,Fto help disrupt child sexual abuse in
OL,11,Fprivate messages.
OL,13,FData provided to the NSPCC by 45 UK
OL,14,Fpolice forces showed that 7,062 sexual
OL,15,Fcommunication with a child offences
OL,16,Fwere recorded in 2023-24, a rise of
OL,17,F89% since 2017-18 - when the offence
OL,18,Ffirst came into force.
