OL,3,CCalls for tougher regulation after
OL,4,Conline grooming crimes reach record
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FOf those, the means of communication
OL,8,Ffor 1,824 cases was disclosed, with
OL,9,FSnapchat named in 48% of them.
OL,11,FSnapchat said it has a "zero
OL,12,Ftolerance" approach to "sexual
OL,13,Fexploitation of young people", adding
OL,14,Fit has a number of in-app protections
OL,15,Fto keep youngsters safe.
OL,17,FWhatsApp (12%), Facebook and Messenger
OL,18,F(12%), as well as Instagram (6%) - all
OL,19,FMeta owned platforms - also proved
OL,20,Fpopular with offenders in those cases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
