OL,3,CCalls for tougher regulation after
OL,4,Conline grooming crimes reach record
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FNSPCC chief executive Sir Peter
OL,8,FWanless said: "One year since the
OL,9,FOnline Safety Act became law and we
OL,10,Fare still waiting for tech companies
OL,11,Fto make their platforms safe for
OL,12,Fchildren."
OL,14,FHe added: "It is clear that much of
OL,15,Fthis abuse is taking place in private
OL,16,Fmessaging, which is why we also need
OL,17,Fthe government to strengthen the
OL,18,FOnline Safety Act to give Ofcom more
OL,19,Flegal certainty to tackle child sexual
OL,20,Fabuse on the likes of Snapchat and
OL,21,FWhatsApp."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
