OL,4,Conline grooming crimes reach record
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FJess Phillips, minister for
OL,8,Fsafeguarding and violence against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls, described child
OL,10,Fsexual abuse as a "vile crime that
OL,11,Finflicts long-lasting trauma on
OL,12,Fvictims".
OL,14,F"Social media companies have a
OL,15,Fresponsibility to stop this vile abuse
OL,16,Ffrom happening on their platforms,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
